 "data": "@startuml
' Diagram UML dla Bazy Danych Systemu Rejestracji na Kursy

!theme materia

' Definicje klas (tabel)
class roles {
 + role_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + role_name : String <<UNIQUE, NOT NULL>>
}

class users {
 + user_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + username : String <<UNIQUE, NOT NULL>>
 + password : String <<hashed, NOT NULL>>
 + email : String <<UNIQUE, NOT NULL>>
 + first_name : String <<NOT NULL>>
 + last_name : String <<NOT NULL>>
 + is_active : Boolean
 -- Relations --
 # role_id : UUID <<FK>>
}

class students {
 + student_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + index_number : String <<UNIQUE, NOT NULL>>
 -- Relations --
 # user_id : UUID <<FK, UNIQUE>>
}

class teachers {
 + teacher_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + title : String
 -- Relations --
 # user_id : UUID <<FK, UNIQUE>>
}

class courses {
 + course_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + course_code : String <<UNIQUE, NOT NULL>>
 + course_name : String <<NOT NULL>>
 + description : String
 + credits : Integer
}

class course_groups {
 + group_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + group_number : Integer <<NOT NULL>>
 + max_capacity : Integer <<NOT NULL>>
 + room : String
 + schedule_info : String
 .. Constraints ..
 Unique(course_id, group_number)
 -- Relations --
 # course_id : UUID <<FK>>
 # teacher_id : UUID <<FK, NULLABLE>>
}

class enrollments {
 + enrollment_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + enrollment_date : Timestamp
 .. Constraints ..
 Unique(student_id, group_id)
 -- Relations --
 # student_id : UUID <<FK>>
 # group_id : UUID <<FK>>
}
note right of enrollments : Tabela łącząca Studentów z Grupami (Many-to-Many).\nNiezbędna do śledzenia zapisów.

class grades {
 + grade_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + grade_value : String / Float
 + grade_date : Timestamp
 + comment : String
 -- Relations --
 # student_id : UUID <<FK>>
 # course_id : UUID <<FK>>
 # teacher_id : UUID <<FK>>
}

class meetings {
 + meeting_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + meeting_number : Integer <<NOT NULL>>
 + meeting_date : Date
 + topic : String
 .. Constraints ..
 Unique(group_id, meeting_number)
 -- Relations --
 # group_id : UUID <<FK>>
}
note left of meetings : Reprezentuje pojedyncze spotkanie (np. 1 z 15)\nw ramach grupy zajęciowej.

class attendance {
 + attendance_id : UUID <<PK>>
 + status : String <<NOT NULL>> ' OBECNY, NIEOBECNY, etc.
 .. Constraints ..
 Unique(meeting_id, student_id)
 -- Relations --
 # meeting_id : UUID <<FK>>
 # student_id : UUID <<FK>>
 # recorded_by_teacher_id : UUID <<FK>>
}
note left of attendance: Rejestruje obecność konkretnego studenta\nna konkretnym spotkaniu (meeting).

' Definicje relacji
users \"1\" --* \"*\" roles : Przypisana Rola >
' Users \"1\" o-- \"1\" students : <<extends>> (Profil Studenta)
' Users \"1\" o-- \"1\" teachers : <<extends>> (Profil Nauczyciela)
' --- Using direct FK links ---
users \"1\" -- \"1\" students : (user_id) >
users \"1\" -- \"1\" teachers : (user_id) >


courses \"1\" --* \"*\" course_groups : < Zawiera grupy
teachers \"1\" --* \"0..*\" course_groups : < Prowadzi grupy (opcjonalnie)

course_groups \"1\" --* \"*\" meetings : < Składa się ze spotkań

' Enrollments link Students and Groups
students \"1\" --* \"*\" enrollments : < Zapisy studenta
course_groups \"1\" --* \"*\" enrollments : Zapisani studenci >

' Grades link Students, Courses, and issuing Teacher
students \"1\" --* \"*\" grades : < Otrzymane oceny
courses \"1\" --* \"*\" grades : < Oceny z kursu
teachers \"1\" --* \"*\" grades : < Wystawione oceny

' Attendance links Meetings, Students, and recording Teacher
meetings \"1\" --* \"*\" attendance : < Obecność na spotkaniu
students \"1\" --* \"*\" attendance : < Obecności studenta
teachers \"1\" --* \"*\" attendance : < Zapisana obecność (przez nauczyciela)
